text: Lewis Moist (26 January 1881 - 14 April 1940) was a British swimmer. He competed in the men's 1500 metre freestyle event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1881 births Category:1940 deaths Category:British male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Birmingham, West Midlands Category:Male freestyle swimmers
